translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ"
  1,2,"Lumbili losope lwene alapikwe Allah, M'mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope"
  1,3,"Jwaukoto wejinji, Jwachanasa channope"
  1,4,Nsyene Lisiku Lyamalipilo
  1,5,"Kwele Jikape tukwagalagatila, soni Kwele Jikape tukwaŵenda chikamuchisyo"
  1,6,Tujongolelani kwitala lyagoloka
  1,7,"Litala lya aŵala ŵanya ŵamwapele chindimba, ngaŵaga ŵaŵatumbililidwe (aŵala ŵaŵaimanyi yakuona nikuileka), kapena ŵaŵasokonechele (aŵala ŵaŵailesile yakuona ligongo lya ujinga ni kupotela)"
